text: Saša Mimić (born 23 November 1961) is a Yugoslav rowing coxswain. He competed in the men's coxed four event at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:Yugoslav male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Yugoslavia Category:Rowers at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Coxswains (rowing)
